text: Georgium is a genus of caddisflies in the family Calamoceratidae. There are at least two described species in Georgium. ==Species== These two species belong to the genus Georgium: * Georgium japonicum (Ulmer, 1905) * † Rhabdoceras fusculum (Ulmer, 1912) ==References== ==Further reading== * * * Category:Integripalpia Category:Trichoptera genera
title: Georgium (caddisfly)
